{"tid":2432195,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"京硬推國安法 藉疫延遲選舉  港自由度衰過西非","createTime":"2021-03-04T06:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T07:21:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85b791607d623e14148baeb7578dc94afeb01945","tid":2432195,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/GD5TEDQ7WVEHDKWWA53Y7P2XV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FGD5TEDQ7WVEHDKWWA53Y7P2XV4%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv1Fonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=08e9e53b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FGD5TEDQ7WVEHDKWWA53Y7P2XV4%2F&h=c6321e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/GD5TEDQ7WVEHDKWWA53Y7P2XV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n京硬推國安法 藉疫延遲選舉 <br />\n港自由度衰過西非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sGiHLBBiH1ZGAZ-DVdUbFJaJT-w=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/47QUZHFGIFEWLFGVTBZAURUBMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsGiHLBBiH1ZGAZ-DVdUbFJaJT-w%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F47QUZHFGIFEWLFGVTBZAURUBMA.jpg&h=aeaa2cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國安法立法後，警員動輒舉紫旗警告示威者違法，被指剝奪港人公民自由。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【自由之家報告】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國際人權監察組織自由之家（Freedom House）昨日公佈《2021年全球自由度調查報告》，香港的總評分較去年再跌三分，100分滿分下得52分，低過西非國家布基納法索的54分，繼續屬於「局部自由」（partly free），其中政治權利一項只得不及格的15分。<br />\n<br />\n這份報告評分是由40分滿分的政治權利及60分滿分的公民自由組成，香港在這兩項分別獲得15分及37分，總分為52分，是報告有為香港評分以來最低的一次。跟去年評分相比，香港得分全面倒退，當時分別取得16分及39分，合共55分。<br />\n<br />\n報告提及香港過去一年由於中國。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由之家將中國評為不自由國家，100分滿分僅得9分，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球75%人面對民主倒退<br />\n<br />\n台灣的民主則獲形容為亞洲最強，以94分列入自由國家。報告指台灣在不濫用手段的情況下，有效遏止武漢肺炎在當地爆發，跟對岸「獨裁的中國形成了鮮明對比」；台灣選民也在中國「虛假宣傳」等干預下，仍選擇了「反對兩岸統一的總統」，即蔡英文。<br />\n<br />\n報告指自2006年以來，全球民。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由之家總裁阿布拉莫維茲指仍有望改。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MzTmmqoNM8UVybDCi2ADvhmqbvU=/864x888/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHS6BIS5AZFTVLCYTHV4LDIK7Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMzTmmqoNM8UVybDCi2ADvhmqbvU%3D%2F864x888%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHS6BIS5AZFTVLCYTHV4LDIK7Q.gif&h=18ecaf83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a47f6cd9c336ce0cf5d8f4966fd7ed85e43aad72","tid":2432195,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"Xianggang: 評分方法唔科學"},{"pid":"7db7591f340734980bf35080c85f06c13ea61dcb","tid":2432195,"uid":363016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"星加坡得咁低？"},{"pid":"1c5b5a015e63af34d4965013db8fbd8aab61cb99","tid":2432195,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"台灣今次真係脫亞入歐了"},{"pid":"9ba3c1f5608d9b75a9d3b7a75ff1f02e01c68baf","tid":2432195,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7db7591f340734980bf35080c85f06c13ea61dcb","tid":2432195,"uid":363016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"星加坡得咁低？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"同香港一鳩樣"},{"pid":"7dc79229567b147cd36c5269967c11642b8bb3b8","tid":2432195,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"台灣94分 !  小英又嬴 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cl